Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I clearly told you all goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never return to the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think they'd be happy to be alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,knowing that it was because their\Nfriend had to sacrifice herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they know why you left them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll follow you to the depths\Nof hell and take out your enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you guys who don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the slightest desire to be rescued!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making a racket for, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen Kenpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noodle Stake Knocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Epluchage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Con...vert!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:02.90,On Top,sign,0000,0000,0000,,"Convert"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:09.26,On Top,sign,0000,0000,0000,,"Pervert"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body should be in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style Sword Draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rashomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Sea King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Further ahead on this railway...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lies the one who cut that thing up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All, go back to the front cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I fell for the enemy's scheme...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a blunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravest blunder of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, gentlemen! Have a nice trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to catch up... with the sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the criminals\Nwe're supposed to escort
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are set free upon the world again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much blood and how many
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tears will civilians have to shed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them that there's justice\Neven in this unfair world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my arms and legs are\Ntorn off by these raging waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will be sure to protect the\Ninnocent citizens' future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:23.24,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.64,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:30.07,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:38.09,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:45.05,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.95,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:52.14,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.95,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,there's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.61,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.88,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.34,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:10.01,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.71,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.39,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.40,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.31,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:28.61,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:32.12,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.55,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:39.62,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:43.12,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:46.67,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:50.15,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.72,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.52,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:05:03.54,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Clash! Demon-Slasher Zoro\Nvs. Ship-Slasher T-Bone"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a new sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Ship-Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship-Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Ship-Slasher T-Bone,\Na Captain at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cuts pirates ships up like steaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Amazing"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking\Nlike it's someone else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just sit around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!\NGet ready to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better hurry up\Nor he'll slash Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you watching all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you only once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't have simply\Npassed by my subordinates' cars
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that were on the same railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did these guys do to my subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be Nico Robin's crewmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which means that that\Nswordsman is the pirate hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This path leads to the origins of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a captain at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not live on in disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you guys by slashing you in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as our destination
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lies beyond where you stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate crooked sword attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right-Angle Flying Bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He discerned it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold Hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated Ship-Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he followed\Nthe sea train
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the detached cars\Nin this storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your justice is deep, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:10:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we also shoulder all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain T-Bone, who jumped\Nout to sea, is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could've been hit by that sea train by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful about what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain would slash a sea train\Nlike that into two, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that swordsman was quite skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain protected us\Nwith his life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from a Sea King\Nthat stood in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How vexing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's Sanji-kun and\Nthe others who detached that sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are we gonna catch up with them soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're closing in on our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna\Nbeat up the pigeon guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pulled it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's something different after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This smell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is filled with the\Nsmell of those filthy pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is definitely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got slashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I didn't get slashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, if you lack love in\Nsomething as small as peeling skins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what dish you make, it'll taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitchen knives aren't swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I won't cut people with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you should notice\Nthat you lost your armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitchen Knife Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oeil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My eyes are caving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, stop fighting and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Why would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get why the heck you\Nwant to rescue a woman like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't actually know\NNico Robin's true nature, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dents!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep talking,\NI'll reshape your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel like my face shrank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you don't know\Nabout her, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a depraved devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:15:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parage... Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My face caved in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror! I need a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you dent my proud eyes and nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, they went back to how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like\Nthey went back a little just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're guilty of three sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you claimed to be a cook in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you treated food with no respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you insulted our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the very definition\Nof "all bark but no bite."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell what part became stronger\Nafter becoming four-legged,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Waaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna give me a hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing just fine, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now tell me if you still think my\Nbeing four-legged was pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my characteristics back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:18:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend is waiting to be rescued on\Nthe other side of the door behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I say I won't let you\Ngo through, I really mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen Kenpo! Secret technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noodle Cutter Poisonous Kitchen Knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch it, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys being\Ndeceived by that woman, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the lowest of the low,\Nwho lived one betrayal after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and survived until today in the underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decoupage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my hands and legs blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let my guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let your guard down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and make excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you add your last words\Nto them while you're at it, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking that you can\Nstill keep fighting, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just natural,\Nsince you dodged all my attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you don't know how\Ndestructive my blow really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where on earth did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish taking\Ncare of the ramen guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who kidnapped Robin-chan,\Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:19.35,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:24.19,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:29.23,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:33.20,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:37.70,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:42.75,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:48.09,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:52.92,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,and live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:55.72,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:23:03.74,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! I wanted to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back together this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, it seems that she's\Nobjecting to your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment will decide the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scramble over Robin!\NA Cunning Plan by Sogeking!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
